longBusinessSummary: Carraro India Limited manufactures and sells automotive equipment, parts, and components in India and internationally. It offers mechanical transmissions, clutches, hydraulic lifts and planetary drives, and axles for agricultural tractors; construction equipment; and gears, shafts, and ring gears for industrial and automotive vehicles. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Pune, India. Carraro India Limited operates as a subsidiary of Carraro International S.E.
